41:22.426 --> 41:24.462
♪ the night I first ♪

41:24.528 --> 41:28.432
♪ ran away from you ♪

41:28.499 --> 41:29.433
Hey.

41:29.500 --> 41:32.403
Did you see your mom?

41:32.470 --> 41:34.372
Yeah, I did.

41:34.438 --> 41:36.440
♪♪♪

41:36.507 --> 41:38.376
Go back to sleep, okay?

41:38.442 --> 41:39.377
Okay.

41:39.443 --> 41:40.444
Sweet dreams.

41:40.511 --> 41:42.380
Night, dad.

